sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Resource Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant FS as Media Storage
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update resource page
    UI->>LW: mount(resource)
    LW->>DB: Load resource with translations/media (if existing)
    DB-->>LW: Existing data
    LW-->>UI: Render multilingual form and file inputs

    User->>UI: Upload files / mark files for deletion
    UI->>LW: updatedPendingFiles() / markDeleteMedia()
    LW-->>UI: Update pending state

    User->>UI: Save resource
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update resource + translations
    LW->>FS: Add new media and delete marked media
    DB-->>LW: Persisted resource
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
